{"tid":715353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇人有個購物狂老母/屋企人","createTime":"2018-06-24T12:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T23:35:43.000Z","uid":165565,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"db5cdc40274828bcdbb0a54e17030b6d81b51283","tid":715353,"uid":165565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:24:30.000Z","msg":"講明先 唔係瘋狂買名牌個啲<br />\n而係洗頭水啊cream啊零食啊個啲<br />\n見到特價就買 屋企已經有好多 <br />\n例如洗頭水 屋企已經有至少15支 頭先老母見到屈x氏特價又買左兩支<br />\n叫佢唔好買佢又鬧我 老豆同其他人勸佢又唔理 <br />\n啲嘢買完番來完全唔用 擺係屋企等過期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日見到全屋都係嘢又用唔曬真係好節墮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問左好幾個朋友都話屋企冇咁嘅情況<br />\n有冇人屋企都係咁 定係真係得我？"},{"pid":"0858a09d55bf85746690485c770b0e244a778a81","tid":715353,"uid":165565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a100a88b900a94ecfb3175dd1b3abf872fc75cd6","tid":715353,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"我買面膜，屋企最多有成4X盒未開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a0a7a07e4b7ab0ecebf6365caf5474e9d7264c","tid":715353,"uid":165565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a100a88b900a94ecfb3175dd1b3abf872fc75cd6","tid":715353,"uid":151664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:31:57.000Z","msg":"我買面膜，屋企最多有成4X盒未開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"認真你用得曬我真係覺得冇問題 <br />\n但係如果唔得...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd23bc4eee386e5f1b016cc4107c47a01d0c26d9","tid":715353,"uid":38287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔捐/俾人？<br />\n驚佢再買多d返嚟？"},{"pid":"a2866a886f48d39148511cf6294a4e13c0d8520d","tid":715353,"uid":51134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"你屋企應該好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係洗頭水都17枝<br />\n仲要未計其他日用品"},{"pid":"c0874cb2220fc7a0486948f0c9b1e6be44ae6f5d","tid":715353,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:04:27.000Z","msg":"偷偷地攞嚟送俾人"},{"pid":"c5dc86fa26d43e0d3177dfe66ddc15eb030e7ff3","tid":715353,"uid":173797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T13:15:10.000Z","msg":"買實用嘢都算，我啊媽係狂買風水嘢<br />\n買埋一大堆水晶、風水擺設<br />\n成日話又買咗個幾千蚊嘅乜乜乜放屋企風水好d<br />\n又話d師傅話屋企擺個鼓好就去買咗個大嘅非洲鼓嚟擺<br />\n又話衣櫃一定要放邊個方位，即刻掉咗本身個仲好新嘅衣櫃去訂造一個岩岩好放到嗰個方位嘅新衣櫃&hellip;<br />\n因為已經十幾年都係咁，講極都唔聽所以已經由得佢"},{"pid":"53f628fac4fe56b3c110e7ce94d0eea6bc838d27","tid":715353,"uid":155725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 15支洗頭水... 無屋企幾多個人呀？一人開一支一日洗兩次頭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我老母同家姐都購物狂，兩個都中意買清潔用品，洗廁所又有，漂水又有仲分廚房同廁所同洗衫既唔同質感既漂白用品(水狀，泡沫，粉狀，餅)，除霉又有，其他手套呀，清潔濕紙巾，抹布海綿都好多<br />\n<br />\n老母其餘既有：餸(一係狂買肉一係狂買菜，完全無諗過點配搭點煮)，仲有好多鞋，不停買但唔會丟，仲中意keep盒，鑊同煲(超級多未開全新既鑊，但佢都會話無呢隻走去買)<br />\n<br />\n家姐：乜都買大量<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我成日都話佢地買清潔用品間屋唔會自己變乾淨架"},{"pid":"969b928e7af678bc4d10c9091e84dd8a4903b459","tid":715353,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:27:02.000Z","msg":"病黎要醫"},{"pid":"889879bddc7e3c8f9f0f033060d37bb653fde1d2","tid":715353,"uid":165565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd23bc4eee386e5f1b016cc4107c47a01d0c26d9","tid":715353,"uid":38287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"點解唔捐/俾人？<br />\n驚佢再買多d返嚟？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"好想捐俾人 但係